\text{Perimeter}\; = 2\times\;\text{length}\; + 2\times\;\text{width}
2(x - 2)+ 2(2x +1) =  \color{blue}{2x} \color{red}{\bf -4} + \color{blue}{4x} + \color{red}{\bf 2} =43
\color{blue}{6x}  \color{red}{\bf - 2} = 43
6x -2 + {\bf 2} = 43 + {\bf 2}
6x = 45
{\bf \dfrac 16} \times 6x = {\bf \dfrac 16} \times 45
 x = \dfrac {45}{6} = \dfrac{{\bf 3}\times 15}{{\bf 3} \times 2} =\dfrac {15}{2}
\text{This gives us}\;\;x = \frac{15}{2} = 7\frac12 = 7.5\;\text{cm}
43=2(x-2)+2(2x+1) \iff 43=2x-4+4x+2 \iff 43=6x-2 \iff 6x=45 \iff x=\frac{45}{6}
